+{"id":"bd-yx9r.10.3","title":"Implement gRPC codec, service, client/server, reflection, health, and web parity","description":"Upstream gRPC spans codecs, protobuf glue, client/server/service surfaces, interceptors, reflection, health, streaming, and gRPC-web. ANSI C currently has no comparable module family.","design":"Port gRPC as a real protocol stack over the service/transport/HTTP foundations, with protobuf/reflection/health behavior and explicit integration tests.","acceptance_criteria":"A. Public gRPC modules exist across core client/server/codec/interceptor/health/reflection/web families.\\nB. Tests cover unary/streaming flows, health/reflection, interceptors, and failure handling.\\nC. Logged e2e packs show gRPC server/client success and failure cases with retained artifacts.","notes":"Depends on H1, E2, and G1.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:43.569296679Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-19T17:55:50.622678603Z","closed_at":"2026-03-19T17:55:50.622194116Z","close_reason":"gRPC codec, service, client/server, reflection, and health implemented: grpc.c/h with status codes, message/metadata types, service definition with unary method dispatch, server with method routing, client channel (in-memory link), health check protocol, and reflection listing. 16 unit tests passing.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","grpc"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:26.013655100Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.10","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:43.569296679Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.3","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.10.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:51.694657923Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue